# Input
```html
<!-- should generate diagnostics -->

<!-- div with onclick but no keyboard handler -->
<div onclick="handleClick()" />
<div onclick="handleClick()">content</div>

<!-- span with onclick but no keyboard handler -->
<span onclick="handleClick()">text</span>

<!-- section with onclick but no keyboard handler -->
<section onclick="handleClick()">content</section>

<!-- main with onclick but no keyboard handler -->
<main onclick="handleClick()">content</main>

<!-- article with onclick but no keyboard handler -->
<article onclick="handleClick()">content</article>

<!-- header with onclick but no keyboard handler -->
<header onclick="handleClick()">content</header>

<!-- footer with onclick but no keyboard handler -->
<footer onclick="handleClick()">content</footer>

<!-- aria-hidden="false" should still flag -->
<div onclick="handleClick()" aria-hidden="false">content</div>

```

